value: Breeds in southeastern Europe and the greater part of central Asia from Kiev, Turgai Province, Gouvernment of Tomsk, the upper Lena River north to lat. 60Â° and on the Yana River; south to the Dobruscha, lower Ilek River, the Tian Shans, the Altai and northern Mongolia; also on the high plateaus of Algeria and perhaps in Morocco and southern Spain.
